<title>smʿt ạlṣwt bynạdy</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- smʿt ạlṣwt bynạdy ạ̉nạ mạsẖy wrạyḥ lblạdy
 wblạdy jmylẗ jmylẗ mlykhạ yswʿ ạlfạdy
 1- wạlṣwt byqwl yạ hnạyạ rạyḥ ytḥqq ly mnạyạ
 yswʿ qạl jạy bsrʿẗ wạlmw̉mn hạkẖdh mʿạyạ
 2- wạlṣwt byqwl yạlạ tʿạlwạ kl ạlạ̉mjạd hạtnạlwạ
 dạ yswʿ rạḥ yqbl wykẖlṣ wlạ yrfḍ ạ̉y wạḥd jạlh
 3- wạlṣwt bynạdy fyh tḥdẖyr byqwl ạ̹yạkm wạltạ̉jyl
 dy ạlfrṣẗ tẖmynẗ tẖmynẗ hạtfwt wmạfysẖ lyhạ bdyl</lyrics>
</song>